request.description:
Add or remove booking from favorites.

Response:
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Booking added to favorites",
  "data": {...}
}

Get booking confirmation details (simplified view for confirmation screen).

Response:
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "shopCoverUrl": "https://...",
    "date": "2024-03-15",
    "time": "14:30",
    "services": ["Haircut", "Beard Trim"],
    "totalAmount": 500,
    "totalServices": 2
  }
}

Remove a specific service from a booking.

Note: Total amount is recalculated automatically.

Response:
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Service removed",
  "data": {
    "remainingServices": [...],
    "totalAmount": 300
  }
}

Get employee availability calendar for a specific date.

Query Parameters:
- date: YYYY-MM-DD (required)

Response:
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "employeeId": "...",
    "name": "Jane Smith",
    "workingHours": {"start": "09:00", "end": "18:00"},
    "blockedDates": [...],
    "bookedSlots": [
      {"date": "2024-03-15", "time": "10:00", "bookingId": "..."},
      {"date": "2024-03-15", "time": "14:00", "bookingId": "..."}
    ]
  }
}
